- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses a methodology to construct symbolic models, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence. 
- cs.DS (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper deals with networks of switched systems, which can be seen as a distributed system. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper proposes an approach to construct symbolic models, which can be seen as a programming language.
